org.jorlib.demo.frameworks.columnGeneration.cgExample1.cg

Class ExactPricingProblemSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jorlib.frameworks.columnGeneration.pricing.PricingProblemSolver<CuttingStock,CuttingPattern,PricingProblem>
      • org.jorlib.demo.frameworks.columnGeneration.cgExample1.cg.ExactPricingProblemSolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<Void>, BranchingDecisionListener

    public class ExactPricingProblemSolver
extends PricingProblemSolver<CuttingStock,CuttingPattern,PricingProblem>
    This class provides a solver for the cutting stock pricing problem. The pricing problem is a simple knapsack problem. Here we solve this problem through a simple MIP implementation.
    Version:
    13-4-2015
    Author:
    Joris Kinable
